<paragraph id="8BB636C4FFB3FB4C3EAAF814201FF865" blockId="0.[151,1436,1972,2030]" pageId="0" pageNumber="567">Body brownish. Head and pronotum with dark brown or brownish markings. Mesonotum with basal triangles brown or dark brown, scutellum disc brown. Mesepimeron black. Forewing with veins brown, whitish spots on veins.</paragraph>
